originalText.text:
Exceptional Service and Genuine Care from a Top-Tier Real Estate Agent

Finding the right home in Manhattan's rapidly moving and busy city can be extremely challenging and somewhat daunting. Our apartment search with Nick Parker was not only manageable, but also enjoyable, thanks to the exceptional guidance and service he provided. From the beginning, it was evident Nick was knowledgeable, experienced, well-resourced, networked, and, most importantly, kind and genuinely committed to understanding our preferences and needs. Nick listened to our list of essentials, and rather than overwhelming us with endless options, he applied his keen understanding of navigating the complex NYC real estate market to narrow down possibilities and provide highly qualified and applicable choices for us to consider. Nick saved us time, a valuable element in real estate sales, and genuinely cared about our interests and happiness. Nick is polite, professional, dedicated, and considerate, making every interaction a pleasure from the first visit to the final walk-through. Nick prioritized our real estate needs, and he went above and beyond to help us ensure we made the right decision for our family. We highly recommend using Nick and Caroline Parker with Eklund Gomes to find the right home for you.

I was a first time home buyer and they guided me every step of the way. If you're looking for kind brokers who have a keen sense of the nyc real estate market, look no further, you found them.
